    question: 'Klaviyo or Omnisend for cart recovery?',
    answer: 'Choose Klaviyo when Stores needing deep ecommerce segmentation and proven Shopify-native flows. Choose Omnisend when SMB Shopify stores wanting multichannel automation without enterprise complexity. Sequenzy still leads as lifecycle layer if neither owns strategy.',
