    question: 'Unique AOV test for this pair?',
    answer: 'Modeled $588 cart (72% margin) and $121 cart (41% margin) with separate incentive caps.',
  },
  {
    question: 'Channel escalation?',
    answer: 'Email 88m → 31h → SMS 3h; frequency cap 3 touches / 7 days.',
  },
  {
    question: 'Attribution caution?',
    answer: 'Hold out 5%; report contribution after discount, not platform-attributed recovery alone.',
  },
  {
    question: 'Migration tip?',
    answer: 'Rebuild cart flow first; parallel suppressions two weeks; pause old automations before enabling new.',
  },
  {
    question: 'Margin math?',
    answer: '$588 full-price $423.36 vs 14% code $364.09 (Δ $59.27).',
  },
  {
    question: 'Who should choose each?',
    answer: 'Klaviyo: Klaviyo is the heavyweight when a Shopify store has enough order volume to justify profile-based pricing and wants every… Omnisend: Omnisend fits merchants who need cart recovery, welcome, and post-purchase live in days — not months — and want SMS in t…',
